---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="❤️ How to Support - Manuel Gil - Software Developer & Open Source Advocate">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 pt-20">
    <section class="flex items-center justify-center py-28">
      <div class="max-w-3xl text-center">
        <h1
          class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent bg-clip-text text-6xl font-bold text-transparent"
        >
          How to Support
        </h1>
        <p class="mb-8 text-xl text-zinc-400">Your Support Fuels Open Source Innovation</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mb-32 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-zinc-400">
          As an <strong class="text-zinc-200">indie maker</strong>, I dedicate a significant part of
          my time to building and maintaining <strong class="text-zinc-200">free</strong> open-source
          tools. Your support allows me to:
        </p>
        <ul class="mb-6 space-y-2 text-zinc-400">
          <li>✔️ Keep improving and maintaining developer tools.</li>
          <li>✔️ Build new features and expand existing projects.</li>
          <li>
            ✔️ Create <strong class="text-zinc-200">educational content</strong> and teach developers
            worldwide.
          </li>
          <li>
            ✔️ Contribute to <strong class="text-zinc-200">open-source communities</strong> and initiatives.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="flex space-x-4">
          <a
            href="https://github.com/sponsors/ManuelGil"
            class="rounded-lg border border-primary/20 bg-primary/10 px-6 py-3 text-primary transition-colors hover:bg-primary/20"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            💖 Sponsor Me on GitHub
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.paypal.com/paypalme/ManuelFGil"
            class="rounded-lg border border-accent/20 bg-accent/10 px-6 py-3 text-accent transition-colors hover:bg-accent/20"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >
            ☕ Support via PayPal
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
